{"version":1,"content":"<html>\n  <body>\n    <p>想要快速了解一天的身體狀況嗎？《KarmaSync》這款強大的健康追踪應用程式，能將你的 Apple Health 資料轉化為一個簡單的每日分數，讓你一目了然。無論你是追求健康生活的新手，還是希望更深入了解身體數據的健身愛好者，現在都能把握限時免費的機會，立刻下載體驗。</p>\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/460x460bb-75-7.webp\" alt=\"限時免費\">\n    <h2>將複雜健康數據化繁為簡</h2>\n    <p>《KarmaSync》透過分析你的步數、活動能量、心率變異性（HRV）、靜息心率以及睡眠品質，生成一個 0 到 100 的每日 Karma 分數，讓你輕鬆掌握全天候的健康概況。它還能追蹤你的體重變化，並提供個人化的目標設定和每日鼓勵，幫助你建立更規律的健康習慣，所有數據皆儲存於你的裝置，隱私安全有保障。</p>\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/1284x2778bb-6-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/1284x2778bb-7-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/1284x2778bb-8-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/1284x2778bb-9-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/1284x2778bb-10-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/1284x2778bb-11-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <ul>\n      <li>應用名稱：KarmaSync: Health Dashboard</li>\n      <li>應用類別：Health &amp; Fitness</li>\n      <li>下載位置：App Store</li>\n    </ul>\n  </body>\n</html>","scraped_at":"2026-05-01T16:58:58.735049+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":370,"images":7,"source":"New MobileLife","fallback":"none"}}